Goal: Calculate the mean of a list of numbers using mean() to verify average computation capabilities.
Goal: Find the minimum value in a list where all numbers are the same using min_value() to see if it handles uniform inputs correctly.
Goal: Multiply two large numbers using multiply() to test the performance on large inputs.
Goal: Calculate the percentage of a number relative to another using percentage() to confirm correct percentage calculations.
